description: Architecture & directory structure for feature-sliced + routes
globs:
  - src/features/**
  - src/routes/**
  - src/components/**
  - src/hooks/**
  - src/lib/**
  - STANDARDS.md
alwaysApply: false
---

- Use hybrid feature-sliced architecture.
- Routes in `src/routes/**` must compose feature UI from `src/features/**`.
- Shared logic lives in `src/components/ui`, `src/components/form`, `src/hooks`, `src/lib`.
- Feature slice layout:
  - `src/features/[feature]/[feature].api.ts` — queryOptions + mutations
  - `src/features/[feature]/components/**`
  - `src/features/[feature]/[feature].types.ts` — types + zod
  - `src/features/[feature]/hooks/**`
  - `src/features/[feature]/[feature].utils.ts`

